@startuml RuntimeViewDebugging
title Runtime-view Debugging

actor "User" as user
note as UserNote
  The user calls https://consurtest.local:443
end note
user .. UserNote

[ReverseProxy (:443)] as ReverseProxy
note as ReverseProxyNote
    Started via "task LocaltestserviceReverseProxyStart" (or shorter: "task lru").
    The reverse-proxy is running von :443.
    The reverse-proxy redirects frontend-calls to http://127.0.0.1:4200
    and backend-calls to http://127.0.0.1:80
end note 
ReverseProxy .. ReverseProxyNote

[Backend (:80)] as Backend
note as BackendNote
  Started in the IDE and listens on :80.
end note
Backend .. BackendNote

[Frontend (:4200)] as Frontend
note as FrontendNote
  Started in the IDE or via "task RunFrontend" (or shorter: "task rf") and listens on :4200
end note
Frontend .. FrontendNote 

user --> ReverseProxy
ReverseProxy --> Backend
ReverseProxy --> Frontend

@enduml
